@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Pet Adoption FAQs";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Pet Adoption FAQs</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="description" content="FAQs page about how to adopt a pet in the Woolly Friends web app." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="FAQs, Questions, Pets, Adopt, Adoption" />
    <meta name="author" content="Kenzo, Lawrenz, John Cee, Jericho, George" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-white font-sans">
    
    <main>

        <div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl text-center text-[#684034] font-bold my-8">Pet Adoption FAQs</h1>

            <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">

                <a href="https://sprouleinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/life-insurance-family-with-their-dog.jpg">
                    <img src="/Images/Dogs/FaqPetAdoption.jpg" alt="Adopted dog from Woolly Friends"
                         title="Adopted dog from Woolly Friends" target="_blank" width="800" />
                </a>

                <figcaption class="text-center text-[#684034] text-l font-bold my-2">A Happy Family with The Adopted Doggy From Woolly Friends</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="border-2 border-[#684034] backdrop-blur-[20px] rounded-xl p-5 m-8">

            <!-- =============================== Question 1 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">

                
                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 1: Do I need an account to adopt a pet?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                Yes, you must create an account with us before you can adopt a pet. This helps us keep track of 
                your application and ensures a secure and responsible adoption process.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 2 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">

               
                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 2:  What information do I need to provide?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                You are required to provide complete and accurate personal details, including your contact 
                information, address, and living situation. This information helps us find the best match 
                for you and the pet.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 3 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 3: Is there a form I need to fill out?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                Yes. Once you have an account, you must answer the adoption form truthfully. The form asks 
                about your lifestyle, experience with pets, and your preferences. This ensures that each 
                pet goes to a loving and suitable home.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 4 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 4: Why do I need to provide so many details?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                We prioritize the safety and well-being of our animals. Detailed information helps us 
                ensure that each pet is matched with a responsible and prepared adopter.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 5 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 5: How long does the adoption process take?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                Processing times vary, but once you’ve submitted your form and details, our team 
                will review your application and contact you within a few days to discuss the 
                next steps.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 6 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 6: Can I adopt more than one pet at a time?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                In some cases, yes &mdash; but this depends on your living situation and experience. We 
                review multiple pet adoptions carefully to ensure the best outcome for both you 
                and the animals.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 7 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 7: What happens after my application is approved?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                If your application is approved, we will arrange a meet-and-greet with your chosen pet. 
                If all goes well, we will finalize the adoption and provide you with all the necessary 
                information for your new companion’s care.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 8 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 8: Can I cancel my application?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                Yes, you can cancel your application anytime before the adoption is finalized. 
                Please inform us as soon as possible if you change your mind.
            </p>

            <!-- =============================== Question 9 =============================== -->

            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 my-8">


                <svg class="flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px"
                     viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="24px" fill="#684034">
                    <path d="M478-240q21 0 35.5-14.5T528-290q0-21-14.5-35.5T478-340q-21 0-35.5 14.5T428-290q0 21 14.5 35.5T478-240Zm-36-154h74q0-33 7.5-52t42.5-52q26-26 41-49.5t15-56.5q0-56-41-86t-97-30q-57 0-92.5 30T342-618l66 26q5-18 22.5-39t53.5-21q32 0 48 17.5t16 38.5q0 20-12 37.5T506-526q-44 39-54 59t-10 73Zm38 314q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Zm0-80q134 0 227-93t93-227q0-134-93-227t-227-93q-134 0-227 93t-93 227q0 134 93 227t227 93Zm0-320Z" />
                </svg>

                <h2 class="inline font-bold text-[#684034]">Question 9: Who can I contact if I have more questions?</h2>

            </div>

            <p class="my-6 ml-12">
                If you have any other questions or need help with your application, feel free to 
                reach out to our support team through our contact page or customer service hotline.
            </p>

        </div>

    </main>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.querySelectorAll('.bi-suit-heart, .bi-suit-heart-fill').forEach(function (icon) {
                icon.addEventListener('click', function () {
                    this.classList.toggle('bi-suit-heart');
                    this.classList.toggle('bi-suit-heart-fill');
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script src="~/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
